sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'ic-overview', templateUrl: './overview.component.html', styleUrls: ['./overview.component.scss'] }) export class OverviewComponent implements OnInit { activeIndex: number constructor() { this.activeIndex = 0 } ngOnInit(): void{ // do nothing } changeActiveIndex(index: number): void{ this.activeIndex = index } }
